  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a developer, I want to easily manipulate `svg` fragments color at run time.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n`svg` colors are handled at startup time were a color argument can be provided per icon instance that will be used to replace all `svg` `prefill`s attribute.\r\nThis prevent having `svg` with colors for only parts of the design and is inherently static. Find a way to fix both limitations.\r\n\r\nReferences:\r\n* [slurp-svg](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/blob/develop/src/status_im/utils/slurp.clj#L20)\r\n* [icons](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/blob/develop/src/status_im/ui/components/icons/vector_icons.cljs#L28)",
